Class StaticJavaASTBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • sjc.parser.StaticJavaV4BaseVisitor<ASTNode>
        • sjc.parser.StaticJavaASTBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StaticJavaV4Visitor<ASTNode>

    public class StaticJavaASTBuilder
extends StaticJavaV4BaseVisitor<ASTNode>
    This class builds JDT AST from ANTLR Parse Tree produced by StaticJavaV4 parser.
    Author:
    Robby
